17enosti pro v\u011bt\u0161inu obchod\u016f. Nicm\u00e9n\u011b je k dispozici mnoho dal\u0161\u00edch nastaven\u00ed. Po ulo\u017een\u00ed zm\u011bn p\u0159ejd\u011bte do nab\u00eddky CheckoutWC ve va\u0161em WordPress dashboardu a prozkoumejte dal\u0161\u00ed mo\u017enosti."],"Create a new %s":["Vytvo\u0159it nov\u00fd %s"],"A new tab will open where you can create your %s. When you\\'ve saved it, close that tab and return here - the editor will update automatically.":["Otev\u0159e se nov\u00e1 karta, kde m\u016f\u017eete vytvo\u0159it sv\u016fj %s. Po ulo\u017een\u00ed ji zav\u0159ete a vra\u0165te se sem \u2013 editor se automaticky aktualizuje."],"Create %s":["Vytvo\u0159it %s"],"No slots available.":["\u017d\u00e1dn\u00e9 sloty nejsou k dispozici."],"Order bumps are assigned to slots but the feature is disabled. Enable order bumps in":["Nab\u00eddky k objedn\u00e1vce jsou p\u0159i\u0159azeny ke slot\u016fm, ale funkce je zak\u00e1z\u00e1na. Povolit nab\u00eddky k objedn\u00e1vce v"],"order bumps":["nab\u00eddky k objedn\u00e1vce"],"One or more slots exceed the maximum order bumps per slot. Increase the limit in":["Jeden nebo v\u00edce slot\u016f p\u0159ekra\u010duje maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed po\u010det nab\u00eddek na slot. Zvy\u0161te limit v"],"Trust badges are assigned to slots but the feature is disabled. Enable trust badges in":["D\u016fv\u011bryhodn\u00e9 odznaky jsou p\u0159i\u0159azeny do slot\u016f, ale funkce je zak\u00e1z\u00e1na. Povolit d\u016fv\u011bryhodn\u00e9 odznaky v"],"badges":["odznaky"],"Customer reviews are assigned to slots but the feature is disabled. Enable customer reviews in":["Hodnocen\u00ed z\u00e1kazn\u00edk\u016f jsou p\u0159i\u0159azena do slot\u016f, ale funkce je zak\u00e1z\u00e1na. Povolit hodnocen\u00ed z\u00e1kazn\u00edk\u016f v"],"Column settings for badges are configured in":["Nastaven\u00ed sloupc\u016f pro odznaky jsou nakonfigurov\u00e1na v"],"This order bump is part of an active A\/B test. It cannot be removed while the test is running.":["Tento dopln\u011bk objedn\u00e1vky je sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed aktivn\u00edho A\/B testu. Nelze jej odstranit, dokud test prob\u00edh\u00e1."],"Remove this item from the slot?":["Odstranit tuto polo\u017eku ze slotu?"],"Assign item to slot":["P\u0159i\u0159adit polo\u017eku do slotu"],"On mobile and tablets, this slot is inside the \"Show order summary\" section.":["Na mobiln\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edch a tabletech je tento slot uvnit\u0159 sekce \u201eZobrazit shrnut\u00ed objedn\u00e1vky\u201c."],"This slot won\\'t be shown for pickups.":["Tento slot nebude zobrazen pro vyzvednut\u00ed."],"On mobile and tablets, the cart collapses and order bumps in this slot will move to the Above Terms & Conditions slot.":["Na mobiln\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edch a tabletech se ko\u0161\u00edk sbal\u00ed a dopl\u0148ky objedn\u00e1vky v tomto slotu se p\u0159esunou do slotu Nad podm\u00ednkami."],"Release to drop here":["Pus\u0165te pro vlo\u017een\u00ed sem"],"No items assigned.":["\u017d\u00e1dn\u00e9 p\u0159i\u0159azen\u00e9 polo\u017eky."],"Add item":["P\u0159idat polo\u017eku"],"Level":["\u00darove\u0148"],"e.g. Why choose us?":["nap\u0159. Pro\u010d si vybrat n\u00e1s?"],"Margin":["Okraj"],"e.g., 10px 0 20px 0":["nap\u0159. 10px 0 20px 0"],"Save":["Ulo\u017eit"],"Add Item":["P\u0159idat polo\u017eku"],"+ New heading":["+ Nov\u00fd nadpis"],"Add":["P\u0159idat"],"(in slot)":["(v pozici)"],"(in other slot)":["(v jin\u00e9 pozici)"],"+ New order bump":["+ Nov\u00fd dopln\u011bk objedn\u00e1vky"],"order bump":["dopln\u011bk objedn\u00e1vky"],"A new tab will open where you can create your order bump. When you\\'ve saved it, close that tab and return here \u2014 it will be added to your chosen slot automatically.":["Otev\u0159e se nov\u00e1 karta, kde m\u016f\u017eete vytvo\u0159it sv\u016fj dopln\u011bk objedn\u00e1vky. Po jeho ulo\u017een\u00ed tuto kartu zav\u0159ete a vra\u0165te se sem \u2014 bude automaticky p\u0159id\u00e1n do vybran\u00e9 pozice."],"+ New trust badge":["+ Nov\u00fd odznak d\u016fv\u011bry"],"trust badge":["odznak d\u016fv\u011bry"],"A new tab will open where you can create your trust badge. When you\\'ve saved it, close that tab and return here \u2014 it will appear in this list ready to assign.":["Otev\u0159e se nov\u00e1 karta, kde m\u016f\u017eete vytvo\u0159it sv\u016fj odznak d\u016fv\u011bry. Po jeho ulo\u017een\u00ed tuto kartu zav\u0159ete a vra\u0165te se sem \u2014 objev\u00ed se v tomto seznamu p\u0159ipraven\u00fd k p\u0159i\u0159azen\u00ed."],"Review Badges":["Kontrola odznak\u016f"],"+ New HTML":["+ Nov\u00fd HTML"],"Name (optional)":["N\u00e1zev (voliteln\u011b)"],"e.g. Free Shipping Promo":["nap\u0159. Promo akce dopravy zdarma"],"HTML content":["HTML obsah"],"(empty heading)":["(pr\u00e1zdn\u00fd nadpis)"],"This order bump is part of an active A\/B test and cannot be moved or removed while the test is running.":["Tento dopln\u011bk objedn\u00e1vky je sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed aktivn\u00edho A\/B testu a nelze jej p\u0159esunout ani odstranit, dokud test prob\u00edh\u00e1."],"This bump is placed here automatically by its Checkout and Side Cart display location. It also appears in the side cart and isn\\'t counted toward this slot\\'s order bump limit.":["Tento dopln\u011bk je zde um\u00edst\u011bn automaticky podle zobrazen\u00ed v pokladn\u011b a bo\u010dn\u00edm ko\u0161\u00edku. Tak\u00e9 se zobrazuje v bo\u010dn\u00edm ko\u0161\u00edku a nepo\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 se do limitu dopl\u0148k\u016f objedn\u00e1vky t\u00e9to pozice."],"This item has display conditions. It will only appear to customers who meet the configured criteria and may not be visible on every checkout.":["Tato polo\u017eka m\u00e1 podm\u00ednky zobrazen\u00ed. Zobraz\u00ed se pouze z\u00e1kazn\u00edk\u016fm, kte\u0159\u00ed spl\u0148uj\u00ed nastaven\u00e1 krit\u00e9ria, a nemus\u00ed b\u00fdt viditeln\u00e1 u ka\u017ed\u00e9 pokladny."],"The offer product for this bump is already in the preview cart, so it may not be visible in the preview.":["Nab\u00edzen\u00fd produkt tohoto dopl\u0148ku je ji\u017e v n\u00e1hledov\u00e9m ko\u0161\u00edku, tak\u017ee nemus\u00ed b\u00fdt v n\u00e1hledu viditeln\u00fd."],"Drag to reorder":["T\u00e1hnout pro zm\u011bnu po\u0159ad\u00ed"],"Remove":["Odebrat"]}}}